Package: libtoad
Section: libs
Architecture: i386
Maintainer: Mark-André Hopf <mhopf@mark13.de>
Depends:  ${shlibs:Depends}, xlibs, libstdc++3, zlib1g, libpng2, libxml2
Suggests: perl
Description: TOAD C++ GUI Library.
 This package contains the files necessary for running applications that use
 the TOAD C++ GUI Library.

