Package: libtoad-doc
Section: doc
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Mark-André Hopf <mhopf@mark13.de>
Suggests: libtoad-dev (= ${Source-Version})
Description: TOAD C++ GUI Library HTML documentation.
 This package contains a HTML reference for programmers that can be found
 under /usr/share/doc/libtoad-doc after installation.
